post.body:
@Nofish I see strange reactions of ZeroNet after upgrade FireFox to version 54 and in about:config force multi-process like in this tutorial: https://www.ghacks.net/2016/07/22/multi-process-firefox/
After this, when I close firefox and start it and next start ZeroNet, I only see little grey blank page.
If I change ``browser.tabs.remote.force-enable`` to false, ZeroNet starts normally.
